  <num>19-4336</num>
  <heading>NOTICE OF THE SCOPE OF CONSTRUCTION PROJECTS (ยง 19-4336)</heading>
  <level>
    <num>4336.1.</num>
    <text>All pre-solicitation notices and each solicitation shall state the approximate scope of the construction requirement in terms of physical characteristics and estimated price.</text>
  </level>
  <level>
    <num>4336.2.</num>
    <text>In no event shall the scope of a project disclose the Library&amp;#8217;s estimate of costs.</text>
  </level>
  <level>
    <num>4336.3.</num>
    <text>The CCO shall describe the estimated price in terms of the following ranges:</text>
    <level>
      <num>(a)</num>
      <text>Less than $25,000; or</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(b)</num>
      <text>Between $25,000 and $100,000</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(c)</num>
      <text>Between $100,000 and $250,000;</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(d)</num>
      <text>Between $250,000 and $500,000;</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(e)</num>
      <text>Between $500,000 and $1,000,000; or</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(f)</num>
      <text>Over $1,000,000.</text>
    </level>
  </level>
  <level>
    <type>annotations</type>
    <level>
      <heading>SOURCE</heading>
      <text>Final Rulemaking published at 55 DCR 493 (January 18, 2008).</text>
    </level>
  </level>
